==============================
Project Content & Style Guidelines
==============================

1 Font style and size

Title text-nunito 20-24px (text-2xl)
Subtitle text-nunito 16-20px (text-xl)
Body text-nunito 14-16px (sm: text-sm md:text-base)
Logo logo-lobste 48px

---

2 Text color and BG color

<!-- import style.css -->

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css" />

.bg-primary (orange)

.bg-primary:hover (green)

.bg-background-main {
background-color: #fff8f0;
}
.bg-background-subtle {
background-color: #fff9f4;
}

/_ Text colors _/
.text-highlight (orange)

.text-title (dark orange)

.text-green-dark

3.  Links
    <!-- import style.css -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css" />

<!-- Google fonts -->

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lobster+Two:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

<!-- import BackButton component-->

        <script type="module">
          import { BackButton } from "../components/BackButton.js";
          document.body.appendChild(BackButton({ target: "main.html" }));
        </script>

<!-- import Navbar component -->

    <div id="navbar"></div>
    <script type="module">
      import { Navbar } from "../components/Navbar.js";
      document.getElementById("navbar").appendChild(Navbar());
    </script>

4. Images & Icons

---

Icons: Use SVG for scalability and color control.
Image sizes:

- Header icons: 24x24 or 18x18 (Mobile)
- Content images: maintain aspect ratio, responsive

---

5. Page Element Links

---

## Page Component/Element Link/Path

Main page Back button /pages/main.html
Favorites Navbar Favorites /pages/favorites.html
Profile Navbar Profile /pages/profile.html
Restaurant Favorite Heart Button Layout only, no interaction yet

---

6. Component Naming

---

JS components in /src/components/
Use PascalCase filenames, e.g.:
Navbar.js
BackButton.js
RestaurantHeader.js
Each component exports a function:
export function ComponentName() { ... }

---

7. Tailwind Style Conventions

---

Button: rounded-full bg-[#FEF3E2] text-[#EB6424] shadow border border-black/10
Hover: hover:bg-[#EB6424] hover:text-[#FEF3E2] transition-colors duration-200
Text: text-[#A0A0A0] font-medium text-sm md:text-base
Flex layout: flex items-center justify-center gap-2
